What would movies be without a red digital countdown timer on the
weapon? No drama at all.

The B-61 did have a green light indicating electrical continuity from
the aircraft to the weapon. It also had a cannon plug to attach an
external control box to allow PAL enabling from the ground in the
event of aircraft malfunction prior to launch.

